docs.summary:
The Hamburger Menu is designed to conserve space by concealing the traditional [Menu](https://support.wix.com/en/article/wix-editor-adding-a-site-menu).
The Hamburger Menu icon is small and implies a hidden list that can be revealed upon user interaction. When the user clicks the icon, 
it expands to display a dropdown menu or slide-out panel containing links to sections on the site.
